album.title: Now That's What I Call Music! Vol. 68

wiki.summary: After charting a top-five hit with “Boo’d Up” on the Hot 100, Ella Mai attempts to strike gold again with her new record “Trip.” The piano-laden song finds Ella deeply entranced by the love she’s receiving in her relationship. Read more on Last.fm.
